00:23:30.840 --> 00:23:32.270
divided by phi.

00:23:32.270 --> 00:23:34.320
And so that would all be fine.

00:23:34.320 --> 00:23:35.377
That's for one dimension.

00:23:35.377 --> 00:23:37.210
If I wanted to do this
