of Xi transpose beta,

00:56:41.270 --> 00:56:43.940
I have this vector
Xi that comes out.

00:56:43.940 --> 00:56:46.740
It's always going to be
the thing that comes out.

00:56:46.740 --> 00:56:49.926
So I will always have something
